The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Henry splits with wife

London: French striker Thierry Henry has split with his wife of four years, his lawyers said in a statement. 

The Barcelona star had married English model Claire famous as Nicole Merry in July 2003, and the pair have a two-year-old daughter, Tea. 

Thierry is extremely saddened by the breakdown of his marriage, the statement from law firm Mishcon De Reya read late Sunday. (AFP) 




